data.description: Sitting on over 3 acres & overlooking the mountains, this Superior property offers private, Montana living. Receiving southern sun exposure (SUNSHINE IN THE WINTER), there is plenty of land to build a shop and/or include a few animals. Upon entering, the main floor feels well taken care of with newer vinyl flooring. The kitchen blends a rustic feel & modern functionality with updated appliances, oak cabinets & exposed log ceilings. The range is set on a large center island, ideal for the home chef. This main floor also includes one bedroom, with a walk-in closet & a studio / bonus space that leads to an oversized, two car garage. The other three bedrooms are upstairs. The primary is spacious with vaulted ceilings, calming views, an ensuite bath & walk-in closet. There's also a bonus area that has a wet bar, allowing for the entertainer to let their imagination run wild & make this their own! Call Danni Moore, 406-396-2442, or your real estate professional to schedule a private viewing.
